                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "It is said that some blacksmiths are apt to bestow their finest weapons upon all sorts of warriors so that they might test them to their very limits. In the process, the most experienced among them have inadvertently learned much about hitherto unfamiliar fighting techniques, some of which have even found their way into their card playing...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Special Rule: Your Support Zone starts with 1 \"Dunyarzad\" card.",
                      "type": "text"
